<HEADLINE>
AMERICAN AND NORTHWEST CONTINUING MERGER TALKS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By DAN REED 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
