   2-graf refer:
</P>
<P>
   VT-GAYS (South Burlington, Vt.) _ From Burlington to
Brattleboro, with hoopla or careful privacy, a scattering of gay
couples across Vermont became the first in the country Saturday to
legally take on all the rights and responsibilities of marriage, in
the first state to let them. By Carey Goldberg.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 2 p.m. ET in ``a'' news file.)
</P>
