   These are among Walter Matthau's most important films:
</P>
<P>
   A Face in the Crowd (1957)
</P>
<P>
   The Fortune Cookie (1966)
</P>
<P>
   A Guide for the Married Man (1967)
</P>
<P>
   The Odd Couple (1968)
</P>
<P>
   Hello, Dolly! (1969)
</P>
<P>
